<title>USA: Candela Corp to market cosmetic laser.</title>
<headline>Candela Corp to market cosmetic laser.</headline>
<dateline>WAYLAND, Mass. 1997-01-15</dateline>
<text>
<p>Candela Corp said on Wednesday it will begin marketing in the U.S. the Skinlight erbium laser made by Fotona d.d. of the Republic of Slovenia.</p>
<p>Candela said the U.S. Food and Drug Administration has cleared the laser for the cutting, vaporizing and coagulation of soft tissue in dermatology and cosmetic curgery.</p>
<p>The company said it has already begun overseas marketing of the product.</p>
